{"name":"Save applications with Google Drive and Twilio with instant alerts","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Save applications with Google Drive and Twilio with instant ","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"From","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Subject","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Receivedat","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"1dac6166-2eb6-4536-b0eb-e9c6801dba6e","name":"New Email Form Submission","webhookId":"b889bef9-8c81-43d6-8c59-81aab78a99cc"},{"parameters":{"operation":"download","fileId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"={{ $json.id || $json.fileId }}"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[54,400],"id":"c2e1a99b-221d-41a3-b4ed-67a5f414c851","name":"Download from Google Drive","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"xlsx","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.extractFromFile","typeVersion":1,"position":[378,400],"id":"539788c7-1f66-4a54-8553-b57a36c4f04a","name":"Parse XLSX Contents"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming email records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    messageId: String(j.messageId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    from: typeof j.from === 'string' ? j.from.trim() : j.from ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,400],"id":"28c93e67-8da6-40b6-a6ca-02bb3e49d6f0","name":"Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"a628ee65-b0f1-4e57-8523-85ebd0c0b7f1","leftValue":"={{ $json.messageId }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operati